00:12:38.360 --> 00:12:39.510
I haven't played enough.

00:12:40.790 --> 00:12:42.510
This is not something to play with, Mr. Sun.

00:12:42.670 --> 00:12:44.360
This firecracker is to ward off evil spirits.

00:12:44.840 --> 00:12:46.320
Chairman Li's missing,

00:12:46.750 --> 00:12:47.510
so what if

00:12:47.870 --> 00:12:49.150
he really has a grievance

00:12:49.910 --> 00:12:51.150
and comes back someday?

00:12:51.480 --> 00:12:53.150
The friendship between Chairman Sun and Chairman Li

00:12:53.150 --> 00:12:54.200
was sincere and touching.

00:12:54.480 --> 00:12:55.480
Chairman Li's spirit will bless

00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:56.690
the Chamber of Commerce.

00:12:57.200 --> 00:12:57.790
That's right.

00:12:58.630 --> 00:13:00.120
Can crossing the fire pit really ward off evil spirits?

00:13:00.390 --> 00:13:01.200
Yes.

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:02.360
Don't believe them.

00:13:02.840 --> 00:13:04.670
They're idiots, superstitious.

00:13:05.840 --> 00:13:06.870
I'm taking office

00:13:07.790 --> 00:13:08.550
today,

00:13:09.030 --> 00:13:10.510
but has no one

00:13:10.510 --> 00:13:12.120
from the other Xichuan powers

00:13:12.550 --> 00:13:13.670
or our stores sent congratulations?

00:13:15.030 --> 00:13:16.550
Chairman Sun is well-deserved

00:13:17.150 --> 00:13:18.200
but taking office too suddenly,

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:20.670
so they may not be ready.

00:13:22.670 --> 00:13:23.320
That's all right.

00:13:25.840 --> 00:13:27.030
They don't know me well,

00:13:27.960 --> 00:13:29.030
but I'll be there in person

00:13:30.180 --> 00:13:31.630
to remind them of me.

00:13:31.700 --> 00:13:33.900
[Wenfu Hall]

00:13:48.110 --> 00:13:48.590
Come on.

00:13:48.830 --> 00:13:50.110
Meatloaf only for you. Taste it.

00:13:54.560 --> 00:13:54.990
How's that?

00:13:56.080 --> 00:13:56.590
It's good.

00:14:03.830 --> 00:14:04.280
I'm back.

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:07.200
You're back. Have some pie.

00:14:11.080 --> 00:14:11.470
Taste it.

00:14:16.830 --> 00:14:17.400
It smells good.

00:14:17.440 --> 00:14:18.160
Of course.

00:14:18.470 --> 00:14:19.680
No one in Xichuan

00:14:19.920 --> 00:14:22.080
knows more about food than I do.

00:14:23.110 --> 00:14:23.920
Let me tell you something.

00:14:24.440 --> 00:14:26.510
I went to every morgue in Xichuan today

00:14:26.710 --> 00:14:28.400
and searched through all the records for several years

00:14:28.560 --> 00:14:29.400
but found nothing.

00:14:29.710 --> 00:14:30.320
I had no choice,

00:14:30.470 --> 00:14:32.590
so I asked my maid and waiter to search with me.

00:14:32.830 --> 00:14:33.440
Finally, I really found Han Shuo

00:14:34.320 --> 00:14:36.830
mentioned by Jia Xiaolong.

00:14:37.350 --> 00:14:38.830
He was accidentally shot and killed by an arrow

00:14:39.440 --> 00:14:41.080
during the conflict between Ma Gang

00:14:41.470 --> 00:14:42.590
and Chamber of Commerce five years ago.

00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:44.960
It seems that Jia Xiaolong didn't lie,

00:14:48.110 --> 00:14:49.630
but where did Han Shuo

00:14:49.630 --> 00:14:50.850
get the Water-shaped Jade?

00:14:51.560 --> 00:14:52.750
He's been dead for so long,

00:14:53.200 --> 00:14:54.300
so there's no way to verify this.

00:14:54.560 --> 00:14:55.710
Han Shuo's ancestors were all tenants

00:14:55.710 --> 00:14:57.990
of the Luo family, a large merchant family in the inner city.

00:14:58.680 --> 00:14:59.710
Han Shuo was Luo Ye's

00:15:00.080 --> 00:15:01.810
errand boy before he died.

00:15:03.960 --> 00:15:05.630
Why don't we go to the Luo's?

00:15:05.750 --> 00:15:07.440
Maybe we can get some useful clues.

00:15:08.590 --> 00:15:10.040
We don't know the Luo family well,

00:15:10.870 --> 00:15:11.680
so we'll have to bother

00:15:12.200 --> 00:15:13.470
Xichuan's Young Mistress with this.

00:15:14.440 --> 00:15:16.080
No need to be polite.

00:15:16.750 --> 00:15:18.040
I just want to ask you

00:15:18.350 --> 00:15:20.200
why we didn't ask Yingying to help us

00:15:20.350 --> 00:15:21.840
with this kind of laborious work.

00:15:22.080 --> 00:15:23.750
Do you know how much dust

00:15:23.750 --> 00:15:25.470
accumulates on the booklet in Morgue?

00:15:25.560 --> 00:15:26.960
And it stinks.

00:15:28.200 --> 00:15:28.880
I've washed my hands

00:15:28.880 --> 00:15:30.560
a dozen times, but they still smell.

00:15:30.920 --> 00:15:32.230
Because it costs money.

00:15:33.630 --> 00:15:34.200
What are you saying?

00:15:35.560 --> 00:15:36.470
No money again?

00:15:37.800 --> 00:15:39.160
Didn't you bring a lot of stuff

00:15:39.400 --> 00:15:41.040
from my house when the clinic opened?

00:15:41.470 --> 00:15:42.470
That's not my fault.

00:15:43.080 --> 00:15:45.040
Jia Xiaolong and the others got hurt often.

00:15:45.470 --> 00:15:47.350
They spent a lot of money

00:15:47.350 --> 00:15:48.080
on treatment and healing.

00:15:49.280 --> 00:15:50.300
Those people

00:15:50.960 --> 00:15:52.680
were so poor

00:15:53.160 --> 00:15:54.560
that they didn't have even a penny.

00:15:55.440 --> 00:15:56.870
We paid it all for them.

00:15:58.590 --> 00:16:00.800
Because I promised Jia Xiaolong

00:16:00.800 --> 00:16:02.870
the Water-shaped Jade in exchange for their safety.

00:16:02.870 --> 00:16:04.470
I can't go back on my word, right?

00:16:06.590 --> 00:16:07.590
So

00:16:08.350 --> 00:16:10.750
you're using my clinic as a charity?

00:16:13.230 --> 00:16:13.800
We're not.

00:16:18.870 --> 00:16:19.350
You guys.

00:16:19.630 --> 00:16:21.320
Find me the books of the clinic.

00:16:25.590 --> 00:16:26.630
Go make money for the clinic.

00:16:27.400 --> 00:16:28.960
Otherwise, sleep on the streets.

00:16:34.470 --> 00:16:35.230
How do we make money?

00:16:36.160 --> 00:16:37.040
How should I know?

00:16:39.230 --> 00:16:39.710
Thank you, Chairman.

00:16:39.920 --> 00:16:40.560
Thank you, Chairman.

00:16:47.040 --> 00:16:48.400
Thank you, Chairman.

00:16:49.710 --> 00:16:50.920
Can't you say something pleasant?

00:16:51.470 --> 00:16:52.440
Let me do it for him.

00:16:53.710 --> 00:16:56.110
Congratulations to Chairman Sun on his appointment as Chairman

00:16:57.110 --> 00:16:59.350
and his ability to do good deeds

00:16:59.960 --> 00:17:01.470
on his own terms.

00:17:01.990 --> 00:17:04.550
Knowing it's a happy day,

00:17:04.790 --> 00:17:07.120
I brought some gifts to the mine

00:17:07.400 --> 00:17:09.330
to cheer up the poor pals,

00:17:09.960 --> 00:17:11.640
but I didn't realize I'd alerted you.

00:17:12.160 --> 00:17:12.840
Steward Wang.

00:17:12.920 --> 00:17:13.510
Yes.

00:17:13.790 --> 00:17:15.470
Distribute all our gifts

00:17:15.600 --> 00:17:16.790
to everyone.

00:17:16.920 --> 00:17:17.470
Okay.

00:17:18.030 --> 00:17:22.120
Thank you, Chairman.

00:17:23.070 --> 00:17:23.680
Jiu.

00:17:24.160 --> 00:17:24.920
Show them the way.

00:17:33.920 --> 00:17:35.310
I used to starve every day

00:17:35.680 --> 00:17:36.640
when I had no money,

00:17:38.270 --> 00:17:41.120
so my brother and I went robbing with hunger.

00:17:42.230 --> 00:17:43.230
My brother offered

00:17:43.230 --> 00:17:44.680
to buy flatbread with the money,

00:17:46.750 --> 00:17:49.070
but I was afraid I'd be hungry the next day

00:17:49.070 --> 00:17:50.270
after the day I'd eaten enough,

00:17:51.750 --> 00:17:53.470
so I used the money to buy a shovel

00:17:54.710 --> 00:17:55.840
and came to this mine.

00:17:56.400 --> 00:17:57.470
I thought if I could dig up

00:17:57.470 --> 00:17:59.160
the Star Gold that belonged to me,

00:17:59.880 --> 00:18:02.030
I wouldn't have to starve any longer.

00:18:03.920 --> 00:18:05.310
I thought you should know

00:18:05.400 --> 00:18:07.310
that Star Gold is hard to find.

00:18:07.710 --> 00:18:08.360
I know,

00:18:10.310 --> 00:18:11.920
so I sharpened

00:18:13.400 --> 00:18:14.120
my shovel,

00:18:14.640 --> 00:18:16.960
crouched at the foot of the mine wall,

00:18:17.550 --> 00:18:18.360
and listened for footsteps.

00:18:18.990 --> 00:18:21.230
The one whose footsteps were more rapid

00:18:21.880 --> 00:18:23.960
than the others must have Star Gold,

00:18:25.200 --> 00:18:26.990
so

00:18:27.750 --> 00:18:28.440
I waited,

00:18:29.360 --> 00:18:29.880
kept waiting,

00:18:31.600 --> 00:18:32.270
for someone

00:18:32.550 --> 00:18:34.790
to bring out

00:18:34.790 --> 00:18:35.270
my Star Gold,

00:18:37.120 --> 00:18:38.120
but I waited for nothing.

00:18:40.360 --> 00:18:41.360
I passed out from hunger,

00:18:42.990 --> 00:18:43.920
but looking back on it,

00:18:44.160 --> 00:18:45.200
I know I was lucky to have survived

00:18:46.310 --> 00:18:47.650
because I didn't know

00:18:48.200 --> 00:18:49.270
that the whole mine

00:18:49.710 --> 00:18:51.120
was being watched by Jiu.

00:18:51.790 --> 00:18:53.960
If I had actually robbed it then,

00:18:54.510 --> 00:18:55.880
I'm afraid I'd be dead.

00:18:58.310 --> 00:18:59.030
You were lucky.

00:19:00.640 --> 00:19:01.710
My luck was okay,

00:19:02.270 --> 00:19:04.200
but my brother's luck wasn't.

00:19:05.680 --> 00:19:07.310
Finally, he couldn't stand the hunger,

00:19:08.400 --> 00:19:09.960
so he stole food from Song Jingye.

00:19:10.640 --> 00:19:11.200
Siming.

00:19:12.680 --> 00:19:13.230
Siming.

00:19:13.880 --> 00:19:14.440
Siming.

00:19:15.120 --> 00:19:15.710
Siming.

00:19:16.880 --> 00:19:18.160
Where have you been?

00:19:18.750 --> 00:19:19.270
Flatbread.

00:19:19.600 --> 00:19:20.120
Flatbread.

00:19:20.400 --> 00:19:21.680
Eat the flatbread.

00:19:22.230 --> 00:19:22.920
Have you eaten?

00:19:22.920 --> 00:19:23.470
Eat it.

00:19:23.880 --> 00:19:24.580
Do you want it?

00:19:24.580 --> 00:19:25.550
Eat it.

00:19:25.750 --> 00:19:26.200
Eat it.

00:19:26.530 --> 00:19:27.070
Come on.

00:19:28.360 --> 00:19:28.840
Is it good?

00:19:32.710 --> 00:19:33.640
What happened to your head?

00:19:33.790 --> 00:19:34.510
Who did this to you?

00:19:34.510 --> 00:19:35.200
Eat it.

00:19:36.200 --> 00:19:38.070
He got hit in the head with a stick

00:19:38.920 --> 00:19:40.310
and became retarded.

00:19:42.440 --> 00:19:42.960
Now.

00:19:43.400 --> 00:19:43.840
Eat.

00:19:44.880 --> 00:19:45.400
Eat.

00:19:47.920 --> 00:19:48.920
Why am I telling you this?

00:19:50.120 --> 00:19:51.310
But I've always felt

00:19:51.750 --> 00:19:52.550
that a man can suffer

00:19:53.070 --> 00:19:54.470
as much as

00:19:54.470 --> 00:19:56.070
he will enjoy.

00:19:57.160 --> 00:19:58.270
If I hadn't lived through those days,

00:19:59.230 --> 00:20:00.880
how could I

00:20:00.880 --> 00:20:01.960
be talking to you today?

00:20:02.920 --> 00:20:03.600
Right?

00:20:06.990 --> 00:20:07.400
By the way,

00:20:07.640 --> 00:20:08.200
this gong.

00:20:10.990 --> 00:20:12.440
Anyone who finds Star Gold

00:20:12.640 --> 00:20:13.470
needs to hit the gong.

00:20:14.750 --> 00:20:15.960
I've been wondering

00:20:16.600 --> 00:20:18.470
when I'd be able to hit this gong,

00:20:19.440 --> 00:20:20.200
but so far,

00:20:20.600 --> 00:20:21.360
I've never succeeded.

00:20:23.550 --> 00:20:24.880
Maybe it's not in my destiny

00:20:24.990 --> 00:20:26.230
to hit the gong.

00:20:47.510 --> 00:20:48.960
I've always wanted to do it.

00:20:49.920 --> 00:20:50.710
Feels good!

00:21:09.070 --> 00:21:11.230
Villains holding sway.

00:21:18.730 --> 00:21:19.800
Almost done?

00:21:19.880 --> 00:21:20.930
You've eaten so much already.

00:21:22.920 --> 00:21:23.880
Have you got a conscience?

00:21:24.160 --> 00:21:25.030
You've enjoyed yourselves,

00:21:25.640 --> 00:21:26.440
but I haven't had enough.

00:21:26.960 --> 00:21:27.640
All right.

00:21:27.880 --> 00:21:28.680
Have some more.

00:21:29.400 --> 00:21:30.270
Is it good?

00:21:32.750 --> 00:21:34.790
It's a mixture of fat and lean meat,

00:21:35.600 --> 00:21:37.160
and the purple perilla is good

00:21:37.750 --> 00:21:38.440
for relieving the fat.

00:21:40.120 --> 00:21:41.030
All right, go ahead.

00:21:41.160 --> 00:21:42.640
Let me ask you about something while you eat.

00:21:44.160 --> 00:21:45.510
Actually, I think

00:21:45.510 --> 00:21:46.510
Wen Jue was right.

00:21:47.160 --> 00:21:48.320
Our clinic has at least a few dozen people

00:21:48.990 --> 00:21:51.960
registering and picking up medications every day,

00:21:52.270 --> 00:21:53.510
but I did the math and realized

00:21:53.750 --> 00:21:56.070
that it couldn't make the balance zero,

00:21:57.840 --> 00:21:59.160
so whose pockets

00:21:59.470 --> 00:22:00.990
did the money go into?

00:22:01.640 --> 00:22:03.160
And who suffered the loss?

00:22:06.790 --> 00:22:08.680
I have two younger brothers.

00:22:09.600 --> 00:22:11.370
Junior eats the most.

00:22:11.960 --> 00:22:13.640
[Hu's Flatbread Shop]
As an older brother, I couldn't

00:22:15.160 --> 00:22:16.750
let them starve, so I asked the merchants back to Shangyi

00:22:17.200 --> 00:22:18.030
to send them money a couple of times,

00:22:20.270 --> 00:22:21.750
but I just took a little bit.

00:22:22.510 --> 00:22:23.200
Just a little bit.

00:22:23.510 --> 00:22:24.030
See?

00:22:25.120 --> 00:22:26.510
They say

00:22:26.960 --> 00:22:28.120
thieves from within

00:22:28.960 --> 00:22:29.680
are the hardest to guard against.

00:22:31.270 --> 00:22:32.680
Don't speak so harshly.

00:22:34.680 --> 00:22:35.640
When I find the Treasure of the Sealed Book,

00:22:36.160 --> 00:22:37.640
I'll pay you back tenfold, no,

00:22:38.360 --> 00:22:39.600
a hundredfold.

00:22:41.600 --> 00:22:42.640
Speaking of the treasure,

00:22:43.470 --> 00:22:44.360
I never asked you.

00:22:45.400 --> 00:22:47.790
You're so obsessed with the treasure,

00:22:48.160 --> 00:22:49.470
so if you really find it,

00:22:50.510 --> 00:22:51.440
what are your plans?

00:22:52.160 --> 00:22:53.070
Give it to my brother, of course.

00:22:54.550 --> 00:22:55.710
I'm talking about you.

00:22:56.070 --> 00:22:57.120
What will you do?

00:22:58.550 --> 00:22:59.230
Me?

00:23:04.070 --> 00:23:05.200
After I settle my brothers,

00:23:07.270 --> 00:23:08.990
I'll pursue the three necessities of my life.

00:23:10.750 --> 00:23:11.750
Tell me.

00:23:11.920 --> 00:23:13.600
What are the three necessities?

00:23:14.440 --> 00:23:14.990
Wine,

00:23:15.680 --> 00:23:16.120
meat,

00:23:17.790 --> 00:23:18.510
and the world.

00:23:20.200 --> 00:23:21.310
Those are my three necessities.

00:23:22.960 --> 00:23:24.200
In all the time I've known you,

00:23:24.510 --> 00:23:25.790
this is the first time you've told me

00:23:25.790 --> 00:23:27.230
what you're going to do.

00:23:27.920 --> 00:23:28.470
That's good.

00:23:28.790 --> 00:23:29.440
What's the point?

00:23:30.680 --> 00:23:31.680
We haven't found the treasure yet.

00:23:32.070 --> 00:23:32.920
I don't know when I'll be able

00:23:32.920 --> 00:23:33.920
to live like this.

00:23:35.070 --> 00:23:37.160
Speaking of which, we've found two pieces of jade now.

00:23:37.400 --> 00:23:38.270
Still missing the last piece.

00:23:39.120 --> 00:23:39.990
What's next for you?

00:23:41.400 --> 00:23:42.510
I have no idea.

00:23:43.990 --> 00:23:45.270
So many things have happened

00:23:45.270 --> 00:23:46.680
since we came to Xichuan.

00:23:47.920 --> 00:23:49.120
They're pretty scary.

00:23:50.230 --> 00:23:51.010
Think about it.

00:23:51.960 --> 00:23:53.600
Anyone related to jade

00:23:53.790 --> 00:23:55.270
is either dead or missing,

00:23:57.360 --> 00:23:59.550
so I always feel like

00:24:00.790 --> 00:24:02.500
there's someone behind it all.

00:24:03.600 --> 00:24:05.470
It gives me the creeps every time I think about it.

00:24:07.070 --> 00:24:07.920
Then let's stop

00:24:08.310 --> 00:24:08.840
and go back to Shangyi.

00:24:10.750 --> 00:24:11.550
No for sure.

00:24:12.270 --> 00:24:13.550
Since we can't go back to Shangyi,

00:24:14.120 --> 00:24:15.270
let's hurry.

00:24:15.990 --> 00:24:17.120
Whoever this person is,

00:24:17.510 --> 00:24:18.550
if we're fast enough,

00:24:18.960 --> 00:24:20.200
he or she won't catch us.

00:24:26.160 --> 00:24:27.990
Leader, Sun Siming is here.

00:24:29.960 --> 00:24:31.710
Go around and see if there are any ambushes.

00:24:32.160 --> 00:24:32.550
Yes, sir.

00:24:39.920 --> 00:24:40.710
Sun Siming.

00:24:41.510 --> 00:24:43.170
What are you doing in my tent?

00:24:44.310 --> 00:24:45.360
Celebrating.

00:24:46.160 --> 00:24:46.880
Celebrating?

00:24:47.640 --> 00:24:48.470
Celebrate what?

00:24:49.880 --> 00:24:53.640
Celebrating that I'm the Chairman of the Jibei Chamber of Commerce.

00:24:55.600 --> 00:24:57.640
Anything to do with me?

00:24:58.400 --> 00:24:59.120
Che.

00:25:00.160 --> 00:25:02.030
I'm sad to hear you say that.

00:25:02.790 --> 00:25:04.160
I've known you for a long time

00:25:04.750 --> 00:25:06.550
and have been looking forward

00:25:06.550 --> 00:25:07.840
to having a drink with you someday,

00:25:08.600 --> 00:25:10.400
but I've never been in a position

00:25:10.710 --> 00:25:11.790
to do so.

00:25:12.360 --> 00:25:13.710
Today, I became the Chairman,

00:25:14.120 --> 00:25:15.880
so I rushed over to share the joy with you,

00:25:16.400 --> 00:25:17.880
but you said it had nothing to do with you,

00:25:17.880 --> 00:25:19.070
so how could I not be sad?

00:25:20.310 --> 00:25:21.440
What are you doing here?

00:25:21.990 --> 00:25:23.880
Can't I just come and visit?

00:25:24.680 --> 00:25:25.470
I've come to be your guest

00:25:26.160 --> 00:25:27.070
and welcome you

00:25:27.510 --> 00:25:28.360
to the Jibei Chamber of Commerce

00:25:28.510 --> 00:25:29.990
when you're free.

00:25:30.920 --> 00:25:31.600
Me,

00:25:32.070 --> 00:25:32.710
the food,

00:25:33.120 --> 00:25:33.600
and the wine.

00:25:34.120 --> 00:25:35.600
I've prepared everything for you.

00:25:36.470 --> 00:25:37.790
Cut the crap. Now

00:25:38.920 --> 00:25:39.920
let me feel

00:25:40.680 --> 00:25:42.160
the flavor of Xiangshui Gang.

