From his words, I can tell

00:33:24.360 --> 00:33:25.310
there must be something strange

00:33:25.680 --> 00:33:26.750
about Han Shuo's death.

00:33:30.640 --> 00:33:32.640
You, idle punk, come and help.

00:33:33.070 --> 00:33:34.400
Who's the idle punk?

